citation: 'Xia K, Sun H X, Li J, et al. The single-cell stereo-seq reveals region-specific cell subtypes and transcriptome profiling in <i>Arabidopsis<\i> leaves[J]. Developmental cell, 2022, 57(10): 1299-1310. e4.'
